{"tid":1295860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《家居維修》五金鋪仲有好多非常有用既野","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T07:52:35.000Z","uid":79024,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f48d016313687a702980999590429b1b1da1c06c","tid":1295860,"uid":79024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"以下係一篇家居裝修用品推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.萬能膠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Md5jVfz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMd5jVfz.jpg&h=f5a58f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膠如其名真係好萬能，可以將任何本身痴唔埋既野痴到永不分離，例如玻璃同金屬或者木<br />\n但係千其唔好倒瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一黎佢陣味真係好臭，二黎佢未乾透果陣真係好黏手，有次係公司架貨van倒瀉左大半桶，清左2日2夜都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n使用方法：<br />\n先將立時得萬能膠塗於清潔後的工用料兩面，等侯10-30分鐘，待該塗層呈乾膜狀後，再加壓力或錘撞擊，即時黏合。<br />\n<br />\n2.釘膠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2GnS48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2GnS48.png&h=bb937a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係萬能型膠，又係可以痴到永不分離，乾左之後會變硬，相比起萬能膠可以用松節水洗甩，釘膠除左用介刀慢慢片都無乜有效清除方法，所以用果陣真係要諗清諗楚，唔好亂咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯一缺點係要買埋支膠槍先用得<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提早排好似出左速乾版但係貴少少<br />\n<br />\n使用教學：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0S0bnR3IMa4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0S0bnR3IMa4&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=4b0e8ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0S0bnR3IMa4</a><br />\n<br />\n反哽工寫住2樣先，如果有巴絲有興趣知既，可以再介紹多啲<br />\n<br />\n支持本土小店 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4201774ad336fdfdfbd0b4dbda5f8584dbd9c06c","tid":1295860,"uid":79024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:14:35.000Z","msg":"開錯台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054c3d968c5721897b72671fa50632b447b9aa3d","tid":1295860,"uid":270489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffbd2c2f785748bc02123e89f93593bfe5e27e6","tid":1295860,"uid":79024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"推推佢"},{"pid":"7357328971054cf3c6edb95db818c57544fb9778","tid":1295860,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"做乜膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}